data.title: Nice store.  Nice staff.  Great food.
data.text: These guys got it down to a science.  It is ALWAYS fresh and good.  I have never been burned at this place.  Made just the way you like it.  Mmmmmmm....mmmmmmmm...gooooood.

data.title: Chris was great!
data.text: After a long travel day, we just wanted something quick for dinner. It was standard Subway fare, but the guy working (I think he said his name was Chris) worked very hard to make sure the sandwiches for my wife & I were exactly what we ordered. Thanks!

data.title: When did Subway get so expensive?
data.text: I ate at the Subway near Residence Inn in Plymouth, and I was surprised that a 12" turkey sub, chips, drink, and two cookies came to $11. The food was fresh, as expected, but I didn't feel it was good value for the money.
